{"tid":1382503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，你哋痴線㗎，第二日返工都仲有心有力","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:29.000Z","uid":120631,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3285dcdafa8c454a631d51caee3fcc5a0763eebd","tid":1382503,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"自己啱啱fg未搵ft<br />\n所以我每次發完夢第二日一定唔會交更返pt<br />\n<br />\n經過元朗西環2戰後，我唔係企最前都攰到仆街<br />\n成身肌肉又痛又酸，根本郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但諗起好多巴絲返緊ft，琴晚槍林彈雨，今日照常開工<br />\n我就覺得自己好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日去緊西環，有位師兄知我哋係想上前線幫手<br />\n之後話自己元朗企最頭排分享下經驗<br />\n問佢學生定點，佢好淡然話返緊工<br />\n<br />\n可能我廢啦<br />\n但我真心好撚佩服你哋<br />\n無論咩位置都好，都有各自嘅辛苦<br />\n特別係企前線嘅返工巴絲，你哋好撚堅揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝各位返工人士<br />\n第二日要早起身返工都照出嚟<br />\n自問做唔到<br />\n請受小女一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"08b498d05daa35ce4ee71739f221e03f01dc827e","tid":1382503,"uid":84396,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"對唔鳩住 各位手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4aa796c86eff93d012755f048cc4699b9352079","tid":1382503,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b498d05daa35ce4ee71739f221e03f01dc827e","tid":1382503,"uid":84396,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"對唔鳩住 各位手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"唔該，休息！！！"}